text: Regina Annette Taylor"Regina Taylor Biography (1960-)", Film Reference. (born August 22, 1960) is an American actress and playwright. She has won several awards during her career. These include a Golden Globe Award and NAACP Image Award. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Texas Category:Golden Globe Award winning actors Category:NAACP Image Award winners
